  <md:title>Record Transactions and the Effects on Financial Statements for Cash Dividends, Property Dividends, Stock Dividends, and Stock Splits</md:title>
  <md:abstract/>
  <md:uuid>79906ed7-aa20-4e6b-b75e-d2ea741c321d</md:uuid>
