</media>
<para id="fs-idm356147360">Date of declaration, May 12, no entry.</para>
<para id="fs-idm364576512">To record the payment:</para>
<media id="fs-idm371014400" alt="Journal entry for May 25: Debit Dividends Payable 2,400, credit Cash 2,400. Explanation: “To record cash payout of dividends.”">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/OSX_Acct_F14_03_YT02Solb_img.png"/>
