<note id="fs-idm358512128" class="think-through">
<title>Recording Stock Transactions</title>
<para id="fs-idm345696576">In your first year of operations the following transactions occur for a company:</para>
<list id="fs-idm364053536" list-type="bulleted" bullet-style="bullet">
<item>Net profit for the year is $16,000</item>
